Interface ArchitectureElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.nasdanika.common.Adaptable, org.nasdanika.ncore.Documented, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.nasdanika.ncore.Marked, org.nasdanika.persistence.Marked, ModelElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.ModelElement, org.nasdanika.ncore.NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.nasdanika.ncore.Period
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Architecture, CodeElement, Component, Container, Domain, Increment, Module, Node, Person, Relationship, System, Technology, TechnologyProduct, TechnologyVersion
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArchitectureElementImpl, ArchitectureImpl, CodeElementImpl, ComponentImpl, ContainerImpl, DomainImpl, IncrementImpl, ModuleImpl, NodeImpl, PersonImpl, RelationshipImpl, SystemImpl, TechnologyImpl, TechnologyProductImpl, TechnologyVersionImpl
    public interface ArchitectureElement
extends org.nasdanika.ncore.Period, ModelElement
    A representation of the model object 'Architecture Element'. An element of an architecture model.

    The following features are supported:

    • Events
    • Increments
    • Facets
    • Properties
    • Impacted By
    See Also:
    CorePackage.getArchitectureElement()

    • Method Detail

      • getEvents

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Event> getEvents()
        Returns the value of the 'Events' containment reference list. The list contents are of type Event. Events associated with this architecture element. Events can be used as bases for temporals and periods, e.g. other architecture elements or increments.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Events' containment reference list.
        See Also:
        CorePackage.getArchitectureElement_Events()

      • getIncrements

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Increment> getIncrements()
        Returns the value of the 'Increments' containment reference list. The list contents are of type Increment. Architecture element increments. E.g. releases/versions for a technology product or lifecycle for a technology product release.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Increments' containment reference list.
        See Also:
        CorePackage.getArchitectureElement_Increments()

      • getFacets

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Facet> getFacets()
        Returns the value of the 'Facets' containment reference list. The list contents are of type Facet. Facets allow to enrich an architecture element. For example, an increment might have a cost model facet describing different types of cost associated with the increment.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Facets' containment reference list.
        See Also:
        CorePackage.getArchitectureElement_Facets()

      • getImpactedBy

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Impact> getImpactedBy()
        Returns the value of the 'Impacted By' reference list. The list contents are of type Impact. Increments which impact this element. A computed opposite to Impact.elements
